Name: Rank
Description:
Average severity of the fault generated
The scale is from one to nine with nine being the most severe

Name: Qty
Description: Quantity (Qty.): Number of times this fault is generated within time range of whole dataset

Name: Impact
Description: Annualized dollar amount associated with current fault

Name: FDD Analysis Type Id
Description: Fault Detection, Diagnostics, and Interaction Analysis Identifier

Name: Notes
Description: Other notes input by user manually.
